{"tid":1542537,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國泰主席史樂山宣布退休　賀以禮接任","createTime":"2019-09-05T01:33:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T03:56:08.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"21c045c3f04728e2e43ef4b28afa8a125ee585b1","tid":1542537,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:33:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Screen20Shot202019-09-0420at204.50.1320PM_zDP8y_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FScreen20Shot202019-09-0420at204.50.1320PM_zDP8y_1200x0.png&h=12c03310&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日持續受中國壓力的國泰航空，再有高層人士變動，國泰宣佈，主席史樂山將會退休，由太古可口可樂總裁賀以禮，兼任國泰航空主席；但國泰並無交代理由。<br />\n<br />\n國泰的公告指，史樂山將會 11 月 6 日舉行的董事局會議結束後退休，公告引述史樂山指，擔任國泰主席是他畢生最大榮幸，感謝國泰團隊在他任內的支持，「在充滿挑戰的時刻，同事們一直全力以赴、盡忠職守。」<br />\n<br />\n將接任國泰主席的賀以禮則稱，七十多年來國泰航空以香港為家，即使面對挑戰，他對香港的未來仍充滿信心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/國泰主席史樂山將退休-賀以禮接任/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E5%8F%B2%E6%A8%82%E5%B1%B1%E5%B0%87%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91-%E8%B3%80%E4%BB%A5%E7%A6%AE%E6%8E%A5%E4%BB%BB%2F&d=Fy0o8YzXie14Yexn7W6ruc%2BSO5qySt9BI5W58Aqq%2Fug%3D&h=9d59e673\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E5%8F%B2%E6%A8%82%E5%B1%B1%E5%B0%87%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91-%E8%B3%80%E4%BB%A5%E7%A6%AE%E6%8E%A5%E4%BB%BB%2F&h=41aaa2df\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/國泰主席史樂山將退休-賀以禮接任/</a>"},{"pid":"5fb430c98f3467ff8d7159b42300672c86e47bc7","tid":1542537,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:36:27.000Z","msg":"保住航權, 但係冇人搭, bye bye 國泰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c3b3d0ed400dab492c4841b63fc6020dab6d22","tid":1542537,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score